<section sectnbr = "5B">
<servcat sctnbr = "05" scnbr = "02">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70A5206010" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Manual Transaxle Unit Dismounting and Remounting
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A5206010001" page = "2">
<title>
Dismounting
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Open engine hood as wide as possible and hold it using rope.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove battery and battery tray with ECM. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1A06002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove air cleaner assembly. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1406004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect back up light switch connector and release wiring harness clamps. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A5206007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect gear shift and gear select control cables from transaxle. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A5206005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect clutch fluid pipe. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A5306009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove ground cable from transaxle.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove left side engine undercover.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drain transaxle oil. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A5206002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove right are left front drive shaft assembly. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A3116003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Hang up engine with hoisting devise (1) so that engine does not tilt.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A521061.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "62.506mm" ver = "01" gw = "226" gh = "161"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Support transaxle with transmission jack.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove transfer and transfer stiffener. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A3306003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove starting motor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1906002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove engine left mounting bracket. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1406015"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove transaxle-to-engine bolts (1) and nut (2), and then lower transaxle.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A520008.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "59.171mm" ver = "01" gw = "213" gh = "151"/>
</figure>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A520009.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "56.208mm" ver = "01" gw = "213" gh = "143"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Pull out transaxle from engine so as to disconnect input shaft from clutch disc.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A5206010002" page = "2">
<title>
Remounting
</title>
<ptxt>
Reverse dismounting procedure, noting the following points.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Be careful not to damage differential side oil seal and transfer side oil seal while reinstalling drive shafts.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not hit drive shaft joint with hammer when installing it into differential gear and intermediate shaft.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten transaxle–engine bolts and nut to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A5206009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten engine left mounting bracket bolts, nuts and engine left mounting bolt to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1406015"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten starting motor mounting bolts and starting motor cable nut to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1906002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten transfer bolts and transfer stiffener bolts to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A3306003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten front suspension frame mounting bolts to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A2206013"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Never reuse front suspension frame mounting bolt to prevent it from loosening. Be sure to front suspension frame mounting bolt with a new one whenever loosening once.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten engine rear mounting bracket bolts and engine rear mounting bolt to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1406015"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten front drive shaft nuts to specified torque, and caulk drive shaft nuts. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A3116003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Be sure to use new drive shaft nut.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten suspension arm ball joint bolts to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A3116008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten tie-rod end nuts to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A6306003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten front wheel speed sensor bolts to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A4606007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten propeller shaft No.1 bolts and propeller shaft center support nuts to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A3406002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten exhaust pipe bolts to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1B06001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten wheel nuts to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A2406001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten air cleaner outlet hose band to specified torque. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A1406001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Set each clamp for wiring securely.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Replenish the following oils.
</ptxt>
</item>
<list2 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Transaxle: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A5206002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Transfer: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A3306002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list2>
<item>
<ptxt>
Bleed air from clutch system. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A5306007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Check function of engine, clutch and transaxle.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Verify that there is no oil leakage, fluid leakage and exhaust gas leakage at each connection.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Confirm front wheel alignment. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70A2206001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
